snippet: A victory outside the ACC that will catch the NCAA Tournament Selection Committee's attention is rare for Clemson. To get it over the Tigers' bitter in-state rival is even better....
lead_paragraph: A victory outside the ACC that will catch the NCAA Tournament Selection Committee's attention is rare for Clemson. To get it over the Tigers' bitter in-state rival is even better.

headline.main: Blossomgame's 15 Helps Clemson to 62-60 Win Over S. Carolina
